<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f7fb; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #0B1220;">
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="background-color: #f4f7fb; padding: 24px 0;">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="max-width: 640px; background-color: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #d7dee8; border-radius: 18px; overflow: hidden;">
            <tr>
              <td style="background-color: #0B1220; padding: 28px 32px; text-align: center;">
                <h1 style="margin: 0; color: #ffffff; font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.2;">
                  Welcome to Mom's Computer
                </h1>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 32px;">
                <p style="margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
                  Hi <%= @first_name %>,
                </p>

                <p style="margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
                  Welcome to Mom's Computer. Your account has been created successfully, and you're ready to start using the app.
                </p>

                <p style="margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
                  Inside the app, you can:
                </p>

                <ul style="margin: 0 0 20px 20px; padding: 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; color: #0B1220;">
                  <li>Ask Mom when something feels suspicious</li>
                  <li>Email or text Mom for non-urgent help</li>
                  <li>Manage your account and profile settings</li>
                </ul>

                <p style="margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
                  If you ever need help, just reply to this email or reach out to support.
                </p>

                <p style="margin: 24px 0 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
                  We're glad you're here,<br>
                  <strong>Mom's Computer</strong>
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 20px 32px; background-color: #f8fbff; border-top: 1px solid #e8eef7; text-align: center;">
                <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; color: #667085;">
                  Mom's Computer Scam Helpline
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>